Hi Team, I added the card for the payment but I dont see any option to add the funds. Can you please help here?

Hi there! It sounds like you're trying to add funds to your account. Currently, the ad credit functionality is not available for newly created accounts by default. To enable this feature, your account must complete and pass business verification, and accumulate over $5,000 in spend. If you meet these conditions, you can establish a relationship with an Account Manager who can request the ad credit functionality for you. If you have any more questions or need further assistance, feel free to reach out!
How to pass the business verification process? I dont see any such option in my ad manager account

To pass the business verification process, you'll need to provide some specific information. Please email the following details to adsupport@newsbreak.com with the subject line: Business Verification:

- Company's full address
- Company's legal entity name
- Company's EHID or DUNS number
- Primary contact person's name
- Company's phone number

Once you send this information, our team will conduct a thorough review and update you on your account status. Let me know if there's anything else I can assist you with!
You're welcome! If you have any more questions or need further assistance, feel free to reach out. Have a great day!
